dct_title_s: Brazil--north coast, Rio Pará, Porto de Belém (Raster Image)
dct_description_sm: Prepared and published by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. "From a Brazilian chart of 2001." "Copyright 2004 by the United States government. No copyright claimed under Title 17 U.S.C." "Soundings in meters." Shipping list no.: 2009-0002-S. Place names in Portoguese with glossary in English. Includes tidal information. Map No. 24294.
This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes. Downloadable data are provided in native coordinate system or projection.
